name: androidpublisher_users_list
description: Lists all users with access to a developer account.

parent.description: Required. The developer account to fetch users from. Format: developers/{developer}

pageToken.description: A token received from a previous call to this method, in order to retrieve further results.

fields.description: Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.

oauth_token.description: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.

prettyPrint.description: Returns response with indentations and line breaks.

quotaUser.description: Available to use for quota purposes for server-side applications. Can be any arbitrary string assigned to a user, but should not exceed 40 characters.

$block: A response containing one or more users with access to an account.

$ul: **nextPageToken**: A token to pass to subsequent calls in order to retrieve subsequent results. This will not be set if there are no more results to return.
